{"tid":1158822,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"史達寧承認是曼聯球迷","createTime":"2019-05-17T08:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T12:14:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"916ff411b2b38d84159d93cdfedeeeaf39b556c2","tid":1158822,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"24歲的史達寧是曼城今季英超封王的主力，不過這位英格蘭球星說，自己青少年時代其實是曼聯球迷。<br />\n<br />\n史達寧今季攻入17球及交出10次助攻，是曼城的絕對主力，最後幫助球隊拿到98分壓過利物浦贏得英超冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n史達寧說，他曾經是曼聯球迷，去了現場看2007年足總盃決賽車路士擊敗曼聯一役：「我也許不應該現在講，但我曾經是曼聯球迷，有舊的曼聯波衫，是他們贏足總盃那一屆的波衫。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=f9f5eafe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"b4ed7e9c39f0e5ad73d9fb15c1794afd22b0102a","tid":1158822,"uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"死獌狗斷腳啦，屌你老母"},{"pid":"5a0c95c30466831b15d4ecca96edeefe1874e187","tid":1158822,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"幫曼市爭光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27438350e789182951347d5e334fa99de221fc19","tid":1158822,"uid":251052,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"曼聯球迷 踢利物浦同曼城"},{"pid":"15b2925ef2bbe93f57d2e36e8d53ba99518c1ae2","tid":1158822,"uid":134692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"250<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b48126c9f10fd85cb9f97b47a9cd985b896ff8","tid":1158822,"uid":9411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"go mu la diu"},{"pid":"158ef780a8cf86ff78577d743837170608b27162","tid":1158822,"uid":89037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"250真係好啱你條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sm